##  Usage

1. Run `python main.py`
2. A webcam window will open — position your hand clearly in front of the camera
3. Use gestures from the table above to control the mouse
4. Press `q` to quit the application

**Tips for best results:**
- Use in a well-lit environment
- Keep your hand within the camera frame
- Maintain a distance of 30–60 cm from the webcam
- Use a plain or low-clutter background for better detection

