## ⚙️ Configuration

Edit `config.py` to tune the behavior:

```python
# Webcam settings
CAMERA_INDEX = 0          # 0 = default webcam, 1 = external webcam

# Screen resolution (auto-detected if left as None)
SCREEN_WIDTH = None
SCREEN_HEIGHT = None

# Mouse sensitivity (higher = faster cursor movement)
SMOOTHENING = 7

# Frame region used for cursor mapping (reduces edge jitter)
FRAME_REDUCTION = 100

# Detection confidence thresholds
MIN_DETECTION_CONFIDENCE = 0.8
MIN_TRACKING_CONFIDENCE = 0.8

# Click distance threshold (pixels between fingertips to trigger click)
CLICK_THRESHOLD = 40
```

