## 🔧 Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---|---|
| Webcam not opening | Check `CAMERA_INDEX` in `config.py` — try `1` instead of `0` |
| Hand not detected | Improve lighting; ensure your hand is fully visible |
| Cursor moving too fast | Increase `SMOOTHENING` value in `config.py` |
| Cursor moving too slow | Decrease `SMOOTHENING` value in `config.py` |
| PyAutoGUI fails on macOS | Grant Accessibility permissions to Terminal in System Preferences |
| MediaPipe import error | Re-install: `pip install mediapipe --upgrade` |
| Laggy performance | Reduce webcam resolution in `main.py` via `cap.set(3, 640)` |

